{"tid":2367129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国「就地過年」標語重口味：「帶病回鄉不孝兒郎，傳染爹娘喪盡天良」","createTime":"2021-01-15T05:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T06:42:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1973b1247fc609e9b8597e4f167e32eb0318dad8","tid":2367129,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"中國多地近日疫情轉趨嚴峻，許多社區或企業積極宣導「就地過年」，有些標語訴諸感情牌，但未考慮用字遣字，警告「帶病回鄉不孝兒郎，傳染爹娘喪盡天良」，引來網友批評太惡毒。<br />\n<br />\n綜合香港星島日報等陸港媒體今(15)日報導，為避免2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫情隨著春運擴散，中國國家發改委等多部門日前發布意見，要求各地、各單位積極引導錯峰出行，倡導職工就地過節，29個省市區隨後發出「就地過年」倡議。<br />\n<br />\n不過，春節回家是許多出外工作者每年的頭等大事，勸人不返鄉並非易事，一些社區或公民營企業近日因此掛出各類宣傳標語，有些動之以情，例如「留在當地過個年，不給家人添麻煩」、「今年春節不回家，過完春節看爸媽」、「沒有攀比，沒有糾結，唯有留守，逃過此劫！」、「是否被逼婚？是否被相親？何以解憂，唯有留守！」<br />\n<br />\n除了打感情牌，還有經濟誘惑，包括「今年過年不回家，二月收入更可觀」、「今年過節不回家，待在公司掙錢花」、「回家是冒險，錢包還會扁！過年留公司，親情不會減」。<br />\n<br />\n但有些標語則難以讓人認同，例如「帶病回鄉不孝兒郎，傳染爹娘喪盡天良」。有網友說，這類標語太惡毒，缺少溫情。<br />\n<br />\n中國多地疫情近日趨嚴，出現「多點散發」現象。<br />\n<br />\n官方通報，昨天大增144例確診，其中本土病例達135例，最嚴重的河北省有90人染疫，其他分別是黑龍江43例、廣西1例、陝西1例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2021/01/15/e46e2b565ebbe000e2704fd365707ff3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2021%2F01%2F15%2Fe46e2b565ebbe000e2704fd365707ff3.png&h=ae679772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2089134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2089134&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=35d4ad24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2089134</a>"},{"pid":"43307ab580dbdc044560bca3b863869ef3572e66","tid":2367129,"uid":55913,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:14:38.000Z","msg":"黨呀 求你處決所有回鄉攪亂國家既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b99cce037279ed550fde3fc3f77378c8d452b0","tid":2367129,"uid":20170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"就地正法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7b7ae4cdbcc2d9afb73f7b48d34e99b26d3d29","tid":2367129,"uid":100999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd2c1a96100578c98893614a0efa75d5a2ccef0","tid":2367129,"uid":290870,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHrSHak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHrSHak.jpg&h=69928049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYa0Q3G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYa0Q3G.jpg&h=d73229a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYdtZW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYdtZW1.jpg&h=bfd03c68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dA9H4oH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdA9H4oH.jpg&h=5d65bd94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"add9272650e7a9ed9680d905cabc92baec80f3c6","tid":2367129,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f56a5f0cb6573dab061e34d7521c6fab0754cd8","tid":2367129,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"文字討論不孝兒郎<br />\n有SEED唔Post喪盡天良"},{"pid":"55817fa20d4ac10b534c280ac3d49415162b09a2","tid":2367129,"uid":290870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYXiCQr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYXiCQr.jpg&h=c1a26373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJ1jng7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg